   7.207      1 Template:Refsrc\",\"  9.09%    6.182      1 Template:Needhelp/zh-CN\",\"  8.83%    6.003      5 Template:Languages/Lang\",\"  7.13%    4.848      1 Template:Encyclopedia-redirect/zh-CN\",\"  6.76%    4.595      1 Template:Version_icon/zh-CN\"]},\"cachereport\":{\"timestamp\":\"20240926183515\",\"ttl\":604800,\"transientcontent\":false}}});mw.config.set({\"wgBackendResponseTime\":142});});</script>\n\t</body>\n</html>\n","rawPage":"{{needhelp/zh-CN}}\n{{languages}}\n{{weapon/zh-CN\n |name=斩矛\n |tile=[[image:fauchard.png]]\n |appearance=长柄镰刀\n |smalldmg=d6\n |largedmg=d8\n |tohit=<nowiki>+0</nowiki>\n |skill=长柄武器\n |size=双手\n |cost=5\n |weight=60\n |material=铁\n}}\n{{redirects-here/zh-CN|极镰刀}}\n'''斩矛'''（fauchard）是{{cnlink|NetHack}}中的一种[[武器]]。它是一种[[长柄武器]]，由[[铁]]制成，未[[鉴定]]时外观为'''长柄镰刀'''（pole sickle）。\n\n== 生成 ==\n[[警卫员]]和[[士兵]]在生成时有可能[[怪物起始物品|携带]]斩矛{{refsrc|src/makemon.c|194|version=NetHack 3.6.7}} 。\n\n== 策略 ==\n斩矛的伤害和[[阔头枪]]差不多，不过重量更轻（60 {{cnlink|aum}}），相对来说也更常见一点。\n\n== 历史 ==\n斩矛最初于[[NetHack 1.3d]]加入游戏。\n\n== 起源 ==\n{{wikipedia/zh-CN|Fauchard}}\n[[Image:Fauchards.png|thumb|right|斩矛]]\n斩矛是一种在11至17世纪期间在欧洲出现的武器，它拥有类似于大镰刀的弯曲刀刃，可用于劈砍或突刺。其英文名“fauchard”来自早期法语。\n\n==Variants==\n{{translation/zh-CN|n}}\n===dNetHack===\nIn [[dNetHack]] and [[notdNetHack]], [[dNetHack artifacts#Webweaver's Crook|Webweaver's Crook]] is a lawful [[artifact]] fauchard that favors [[Drow (starting race)|drow]], and acts as the alternate [[quest artifact]] for traitor male drow [[Priest]]s, [[Ranger]]s, [[Rogue]]s, and [[Wizard]]s. It grants +1 [[to-hit]] and double damage, and can be used in melee range without any penalty. Attacks with Webweaver's Crook snare the target in [[web]]s and are automatically given [[sleep]], [[blind]]ing and [[paralysis]] poison, without any penalty to [[alignment record]].\n\n===NetHack Fourk===\n[[NetHack Fourk]] removes the fauchard and many other polearms.\n\n===xNetHack===\n[[xNetHack]] removes the fauchard and many other polearms.\n\n===EvilHack===\nIn [[EvilHack]], a fauchard can be created at a [[Forge (dungeon feature)|forge]] by combining a [[saber]] and a [[spear]].\n\n== 百科文本 ==\n{{encyclopedia-redirect/zh-CN|长柄武器}}\n\n== 引用及注释 ==\n<references/>\n{{nethack-367/zh-CN}}\n[[Category:Weapons/zh-CN|ZHANMAO]]"}